--- Release version 1.02 (09.08.2002) -------------------------------------

1. Fix bug in RIPCServerMonitor

--- Release version 1.03 (07.05.2003) -------------------------------------

1. Add RIPCSesssion.isOk() and RIPCSession.getErrorText() methods to obtain information about the connection status

--- Release version 1.04 (19.05.2003) -------------------------------------

1. Fix bug in RIPCQueueStub.get method.
2. Fix bug in RIPCSessionStub.close method.

--- Release version 1.05 (08.07.2003) -------------------------------------

1. Implement priority wait

--- Release version 1.06 (12.11.2003) -------------------------------------

1. Fix memory leaks
2. Make it possible to specify maximal number of connection attempts for session

--- Release version 1.07 (26.11.2003) -------------------------------------
1. Fix bug in RIPCServer constructor
2. Update doxygen documentation

--- Release version 1.08 (05.08.2008) -------------------------------------
1. Fix incompatibilities with the latest GCC versions.
